          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Corporate Political Disclosure Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 to require issuers, on an annual basis,&nbsp;to publicly disclose political activity expenditures made during the previous year. The Securities and Exchange Commission must issue regulations to carry out this bill. </p>]]></text>
